    • duplicate

      DnsServerAddressStream duplicate()
      Duplicate this object. The result of this should be able to be independently iterated over via next().

      Note that Object.clone() isn't used because it may make sense for some implementations to have the following relationship x.duplicate() == x.

      Returns:
      A duplicate of this object.
